WEBVTT

00:06:28.874 --> 00:06:30.771
a number of these other diseases.

00:06:31.133 --> 00:06:35.553
And this applies not just to people
who have been living in the USA

00:06:35.577 --> 00:06:37.561
for many generations,

00:06:37.585 --> 00:06:40.021
but also to immigrants and refugees,

00:06:40.045 --> 00:06:43.727
who, for most immigrant
and refugee groups,

00:06:43.751 --> 00:06:46.852
arrive in the USA metabolically healthy,

00:06:46.876 --> 00:06:48.256
and then within a few years,

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:51.638
they become just as high-risk
for obesity and diabetes

00:06:51.662 --> 00:06:53.743
as other Americans.

00:06:53.767 --> 00:06:57.465
